  goal "Add a minimal Node regression test for issue 759. Create desktop/scripts/engine-manager.test.mjs and add it to the desktop npm test command. The test must require ../lib/engine-manager.cjs and prove: out-of-box is always available; installed agent, codex, and claude commands are detected; agent is the default when installed; out-of-box is the default when agent is absent; an available saved selection wins; and an unavailable saved selection is ignored. Do not implement engine-manager.cjs or change production behavior. Run the new test to capture the expected failing state, then stop."
